data.description: Price Reduction!!!This one is a must-see.  Below $200k, with fresh countertops and spotless vinyl plank floors throughout.  Lots of space for the money and a sleek, fresh look to boot!  Generously-sized bedrooms, an enormous living space, and two dining areas!  The covered patio is off the dining area and leads you from the sliding glass door to the wood deck.  A great spot for your smoker, grill, and a couple of lawn chairs.  Clean, vacant, and ready for a new family!
